fields.name: Nike Dri-FIT Strike
fields.description: Men's 1/4-Zip Football Drill Top, The Nike Dri-FIT Strike Drill Top is made from stretchy, sweat-wicking fabric to help you stay dry and comfortable when practising your skills. The 1/4-zip design includes a streamlined fit and hidden thumbholes to help cut down distractions.

fields.name: Nike Dri-FIT Academy
fields.description: Football Pants, bottoms, The Nike Dri-FIT Academy Trousers feature sweat-wicking fabric to help keep you dry and moving fast on the pitch.Tapered legs keep your feet clear on the ball, while zip hems let you change them quickly over boots or shoes.This product is made from 100% recycled polyester fibres.

fields.name: Nike Strike football
fields.description: The Nike Strike Football features grooves designed for consistent spin when the ball is in the air. The durable casing and rubber bladder combine for long-lasting performance.

fields.name: Men's Nike Therma-FIT Football Jacket
fields.description: The barcelona F.C. Strike Jacket is equipped with down fill, so you can stay warm while you cheer for your team. Its taffeta fabric with a water-repellent finish is durable and lightweight to help keep you dry in wet weather.
